dler(ctx, round_id)\n    57→    }\n    58→\n    59→    pub fn force_close<'info>(\n    60→        ctx: Context<'_, '_, 'info, 'info, ForceClose<'info>>,\n    61→        round_id: [u8; 8],\n    62→    ) -> Result<()> {\n    63→        instructions::force_close::handler(ctx, round_id)\n    64→    }\n    65→}\n    66→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012FZFQthTpmV4TStVPM7FGb","session_id":"efe120e9-7ceb-4e75-b227-230da807bdef","uuid":"79c776fb-0795-4a55-a027-5a1d386b2e84"}
