{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PDMJXbaBCdYxDxMkBiGc1S","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/**\n     2→ * Program IDL in camelCase format in order to be used in JS/TS.\n     3→ *\n     4→ * Note that this is only a type helper and is not the actual IDL. The original\n     5→ * IDL can be found at `target/idl/closecall.json`.\n     6→ */\n     7→export type Closecall = {\n     8→  \"address\": \"8TXq2XyHsk5AAMkoyk5QtG25xyyY7rTMHXrJRHRwjUpA\",\n     9→  \"metadata\": {\n    10→    \"name\": \"closecall\",\n    11→    \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n    12→    \"spec\": \"0.1.0\"\n    13→  },\n    14→  \"instructions\": [\n    15→    {\n    16→      \"name\": \"createRound\",\n    17→      \"discriminator\": [\n    18→        229,\n    19→        218,\n    20→        236,\n    21→        169,\n    22→        231,\n    23→        80,\n    24→        134,\n    25→        112\n    26→      ],\n    27→      \"accounts\": [\n    28→        {\n    29→          \"name\": \"server\",\n    30→          \"docs\": [\n    31→            \"Server wallet — pays rent, will later settle.\"\n    32→          ],\n    33→          \"writable\": true,\n    34→          \"signer\": true\n    35→        },\n    36→        {\n    37→          \"name\": \"config\",\n    38→          \"pda\": {\n    39→            \"seeds\": [\n    40→              {\n    41→                \"kind\": \"const\",\n    42→                \"value\": [\n    43→                  99,\n    44→                  108,\n    45→                  111,\n    46→                  115,\n    47→                  101,\n    48→                  99,\n    49→                  97,\n    50→                  108,\n    51→                  108,\n    52→                  95,\n    53→                  99,\n    54→                  111,\n    55→                  110,\n    56→                  102,\n    57→                  105,\n    58→                  103\n    59→                ]\n    60→         