used(false, paused) | Verify game not paused (line 48) |\n| `rng_shared::pause::check_not_paused` | place_bet.rs:3 | check_not_paused(false, paused) | Verify game not paused (line 37) |\n| `rng_shared::escrow::transfer_lamports_to_pda` | place_bet.rs:2 | transfer_lamports_to_pda(player, round, amount, system) | Deposit wager (line 83) |\n| `rng_shared::wager::validate_wager` | place_bet.rs:4 | validate_wager(amount) | Enforce min/max wager (line 45) |\n| `rng_shared::escrow::transfer_lamports_from_pda` | settle_round.rs:2 | transfer_lamports_from_pda(round, recipient, payout) | Pay winners + treasury (lines 167, 174, 191, 205) |\n| `rng_shared::fees::calculate_net_payout` | settle_round.rs:3 | calculate_net_payout(total_pool) | Compute fee & net payout (line 129) |\n| `rng_shared::escrow::transfer_lamports_from_pda` | timeout_refund.rs:2 | transfer_lamports_from_pda(round, player, amount) | Refund bets (lines 81, 91) |\n| `rng_shared::timeout::is_expired` | timeout_refund.rs:3 | is_expired(deadline, now) | Check deadline passed (line 57) |\n| `rng_shared::escrow::transfer_lamports_from_pda` | force_close.rs:2 | transfer_lamports_from_pda(round, player, amount) | Refund bets (lines 74, 84) |\n\n**Shared crate dependencies in Cargo.toml**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/Cargo.toml:12`\n```\nrng-shared = { workspace = true }\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Fee Calculation Logic\n\n**Location**: Shared crate at `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/fees.rs`\n\n**Constants** (lines 1-11):\n```rust\npub const MAX_FEE_BPS: u16 = 1000;          // Safety cap\npub const TOTAL_FEE_BPS: u16 = 300;         // 3%\npub const REVENUE_BPS: u16 = 200;           // 200 bps revenue\npub const RAKEBACK_BPS: u16 = 70;           // 70 bps rakeback\npub const CHEST_BPS: u16 = 30;              // 30 bps chest treasury\n```\n\n**Public Functions**:\n\n1. **`calculate_fee(amount: u64) -> u64`** (lines 18-20):\n   - Formula: `(amount * 300 / 10000)` — rounds down, favors player\n   - Used in: settle_round.rs:129 as `calculate_net_payout(total_pool)`\n\n2. **`calculate_net_payout(pool: u64) -> (u64, u64)`** (lines 25-28):\n   - Returns `(fee, net_payout)` where `net_payout = pool - fee`\n   - Called in settle_round handler (line 129)\n   - Fee goes to treasury; net_payout distributed to winners\n\n3. **`split_fee(fee: u64) -> (u64, u64, u64)`** (lines 31-36):\n   - Returns `(revenue, rakeback, chest)`\n   - Not currently used in closecall (future integration)\n   - Remainder goes to chest to avoid rounding loss\n\n**Integration in settle_round** (settle_round.rs:125-130):\n```rust\nlet total_pool = round.green_pool + round.red_pool;\nlet (fee, net_pool) = calculate_net_payout(total_pool);\ntotal_fee = fee;\n// ... distribute net_pool to winners\n// ... transfer fee to treasury (line 174)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 6. Phase/State Machine Enums\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/state.rs`\n\n**1. CloseCallPhase** (lines 12-19):\n```rust\npub enum CloseCallPhase {\n    Open,      // Round is open for bets (first 30s of candle)\n    Settled,   // Outcome determined, payouts distributed\n    Refunded,  // All bets refunded (invalid round, timeout, or force close)\n}\n```\n\n**Transitions**:\n- `Open` → `Settled` (settle_round handler, line 239) on decisive outcome\n- `Open` → `Refunded` (settle_round handler, line 237) on refund outcome\n- `Open` → `Refunded` (timeout_refund handler, line 96) on deadline elapsed\n- `Open` → `Refunded` (force_close handler, line 89) on admin force close\n\n**2. Outcome** (lines 23-28):\n```rust\npub enum Outcome {\n    Pending,  // Not yet determined\n    Green,    // Green (bull) side won\n    Red,      // Red (bear) side won\n    Refund,   // Refunded (invalid round, no winner, or timeout)\n}\n```\n\n**Determination logic** (settle_round.rs:108-117):\n```rust\nlet outcome = if total_count == 0 {\n    Outcome::Refund\n} else if !has_both_sides || total_count == 1 || close_price == open_price {\n    Outcome::Refund\n} else if close_price > open_price {\n    Outcome::Green\n} else {\n    Outcome::Red\n};\n```\n\n**3. BetSide** (lines 5-8):\n```rust\npub enum BetSide {\n    Green,  // Bull side\n    Red,    // Bear side\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. Error Codes\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/error.rs`\n\nAll error codes use `#[error_code]` which adds 6000 base offset (Anchor convention).\n\n| Error Code | Final Code | Message | Context |\n|-----------|-----------|---------|---------|\n| `WagerBelowMinimum = 100` | **6100** | \"Wager amount below minimum\" | place_bet validation (line 45) |\n| `InvalidPhase` | **6101** | \"Round is not in the expected phase\" | phase check (lines 40, 44, 62) |\n| `BettingClosed` | **6102** | \"Betting window has closed\" | time check (line 43) |\n| `PlayerAlreadyBet` | **6103** | \"Player already has a bet in this round\" | one-bet-per-player check (line 64) |\n| `MaxEntriesReached` | **6104** | \"Maximum entries per side reached\" | max_entries check (lines 71, 77) |\n| `InvalidSide` | **6105** | \"Invalid bet side: must be 0 (Green) or 1 (Red)\" | side validation (line 50) |\n| `CandleNotClosed` | **6106** | \"Candle has not closed yet\" | settle_round timing (line 83) |\n| `InvalidPriceAccount` | **6107** | \"Invalid Pyth price account data\" | pyth.rs deserialization (lines 65, 74) |\n| `PriceFeedMismatch` | **6108** | \"Pyth feed ID does not match expected feed\" | pyth.rs feed validation (line 69) |\n| `PriceTooStale` | **6109** | \"Price data is too stale\" | pyth.rs freshness check (line 74) |\n| `DeadlineNotReached` | **6110** | \"Resolve deadline has not elapsed yet\" | timeout_refund timing (line 58) |\n| `AccountMismatch` | **6111** | \"Account key does not match expected value\" | account validation (lines 70, 75, 149, 188) |\n| `ArithmeticOverflow` | **6112** | \"Arithmetic overflow\" | checked