_config.rs:27)\n- Stored in `CloseCallConfig.max_entries_per_side: u8` (state.rs:51)\n- Runtime limit enforced in place_bet (length check against config value)\n- Hard max in state via `#[max_len(32)]` — cannot exceed 32 per side\n\n---\n\n### 10. Timeout / Refund Logic\n\n**Location**: Multiple instruction files\n\n**A. Timeout Constants** (create_round.rs:12-16):\n```rust\npub const CANDLE_DURATION_SECS: i64 = 60;      // 1-minute candle\npub const RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS: i64 = 300;     // 5 minutes after candle close\n```\n\n**Total deadline** = `created_at + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS + RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS` = 360 seconds (6 minutes) from round creation\n\n**B. Timeline Setup** (create_round.rs:59-74):\n```rust\nlet betting_window = ctx.accounts.config.betting_window_secs as i64;\nround.created_at = now;\nround.betting_ends_at = now + betting_window;\nround.resolve_deadline = now + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS + RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS;\n```\n\n**C. Settle Round Timing Check** (settle_round.rs:78-83):\n```rust\nlet now = Clock::get()?.unix_timestamp;\nlet candle_close_time = round.created_at + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS;\nrequire!(now >= candle_close_time, CloseCallError::CandleNotClosed);\n```\n- Must wait ≥ 60 seconds after round creation to settle\n\n**D. Timeout Refund Logic** (timeout_refund.rs:39-99):\n```rust\nlet now = Clock::get()?.unix_timestamp;\nrequire!(\n    is_expired(round.resolve_deadline, now),\n    CloseCallError::DeadlineNotReached\n);\n```\n- Uses `is_expired(deadline, now)` from `rng_shared::timeout` (returns `now >= deadline`)\n- If deadline passed and round still `Open`, anyone can call timeout_refund\n- Refunds all bets (green + red) in full\n- Sets phase to `Refunded`, outcome to `Outcome::Refund`\n\n**E. Refund Payouts** (settle_round.rs:176-211 and timeout_refund.rs:66-93):\n- Both handlers iterate green_entries first, then red_entries\n- Each player receives exact bet amount (no fees deducted on refund)\n- Remaining accounts list must match entry order: `[green_0..green_n, red_0..red_m]`\n- Account mismatch results in error 6111\n\n**F. Force Close** (force_close.rs:38-93):\n- Admin-only (requires config authority signature, line 11)\n- Identical to timeout_refund refund logic (no deadline check)\n- Can close `Open` rounds at any time\n- Sets phase to `Refunded`, outcome to `Outcome::Refund`\n\n---\n\n## Summary Statistics\n\n- **Instruction handlers**: 6 (initialize_config, create_round, place_bet, settle_round, timeout_refund, force_close)\n- **State structs**: 3 (CloseCallConfig, CloseCallRound, + 4 supporting enums)\n- **Error codes**: 15 (6100–6114)\n- **PDA types**: 2 (config, round)\n- **Max entries per side**: 32 (configurable at init, hard-capped in state)\n- **Candle duration**: 60 seconds\n- **Resolve timeout buffer**: 300 seconds (5 min after candle close)\n- **Fee structure**: 3% total (200 bps revenue, 70 bps rakeback, 30 bps chest)\n- **Shared crate modules used**: 5 (escrow, fees, pause, timeout, wager)\n- **Pyth parser functions**: 1 (parse_price_update)\n\nAll file paths are absolute and anchored to `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/` or `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/`."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a85ed876de74c52f7 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 61154\ntool_uses: 25\nduration_ms: 99794</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"efe120e9-7ceb-4e75-b227-230da807bdef","uuid":"b5ed48d6-3214-40c9-8606-944e8e8279d1","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Thoroughly inventory the Close Call on-chain program. I need:\n\n1. All `pub fn` instruction handlers in `sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/` — list each with file path and line number\n2. All account state structs (e.g., CloseCallConfig, CloseCallRound) with file path and line number\n3. The pyth.rs parser — what it exports and line numbers\n4. Shared crate usage — grep for `use shared::` or `use cra