 `settle_round::handler` → `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/instructions/settle_round.rs:56`\n- `timeout_refund::handler` → `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/instructions/timeout_refund.rs:39`\n- `force_close::handler` → `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/instructions/force_close.rs:38`\n\n---\n\n### 2. Account State Structs\n\nAll defined in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/state.rs`:\n\n| Struct | Line | Purpose | Derives |\n|--------|------|---------|---------|\n| `BetSide` (enum) | state.rs:5 | Betting side indicator (Green=0, Red=1) | AnchorSerialize, AnchorDeserialize, Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq, Debug, InitSpace |\n| `CloseCallPhase` (enum) | state.rs:12 | Round lifecycle (Open, Settled, Refunded) | AnchorSerialize, AnchorDeserialize, Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq, Debug, InitSpace |\n| `Outcome` (enum) | state.rs:23 | Settlement outcome (Pending, Green, Red, Refund) | AnchorSerialize, AnchorDeserialize, Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq, Debug, InitSpace |\n| `BetEntry` | state.rs:32 | Single bet entry (player, amount_lamports) | AnchorSerialize, AnchorDeserialize, Clone, Debug, InitSpace |\n| `CloseCallConfig` | state.rs:41 | Global program config (authority, treasury, pyth_feed_id, betting_window_secs, max_entries_per_side, paused, bump) | InitSpace |\n| `CloseCallRound` | state.rs:62 | Single round state (round_id, server, phase, entries, pools, prices, timestamps, outcome, fees, bump) | InitSpace |\n| `RoundSettled` (event) | state.rs:105 | Emitted on settlement (round_id, outcome, prices, pools, fees, num_winners) | N/A (event) |\n\n**Key Fields in CloseCallRound** (lines 62-101):\n- `round_id: [u8; 8]` — backend-generated ID\n- `server: Pubkey` — server wallet paying rent, settles later\n- `phase: CloseCallPhase` — current round state\n- `green_entries: Vec<BetEntry>` — max_len 32 (at state.rs:71)\n- `red_entries: Vec<BetEntry>` — max_len 32 (at state.rs:74)\n- `green_pool: u64`, `red_pool: u64` — cumulative stakes\n- `open_price: i64`, `open_price_expo: i32` — Pyth open price + exponent\n- `close_price: i64` — Pyth close price (0 until settled)\n- `created_at: i64`, `betting_ends_at: i64`, `resolve_deadline: i64` — timestamps\n- `outcome: Outcome` — final result\n- `total_fee: u64` — fee collected (0 for refunds)\n- `bump: u8` — PDA bump for state.rs:59 seeds\n\n---\n\n### 3. Pyth Parser (pyth.rs)\n\nFile: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/pyth.rs`\n\n**Exported Public Types** (lines 5-12):\n```rust\npub struct PythPrice {\n    pub price: i64,\n    pub conf: u64,\n    pub exponent: i32,\n    pub publish_time: i64,\n}\n```\n\n**Exported Public Function** (lines 54-82):\n```rust\npub fn parse_price_update(\n    account_data: &[u8],\n    expected_feed_id: &[u8; 32],\n    max_age_secs: i64,\n    current_time: i64,\n) -> Result<PythPrice>\n```\n\n**What it does** (lines 54-82):\n1. Validates account data length > 8 (after 8-byte Anchor discriminator)\n2. Deserializes as `PriceUpdateV2Inner` (Borsh format)\n3. Verifies feed_id matches expected value (line 67-69)\n4. Checks price freshness: `age <= max_age_secs` (line 73-74)\n5. Returns `PythPrice` with price, conf, exponent, publish_time\n\n**Internal Support Types** (not exported):\n- `PriceFeedMessage` (line 21) — feed_id, price, conf, exponent, publish_time, prev_publish_time, ema_price, ema_conf\n- `VerificationLevel` (line 33) — enum: Partial { num_signatures }, Full\n- `PriceUpdateV2Inner` (line 39) — write_authority, verification_level, price_message, posted_slot\n\n**Used in**:\n- `create_round` → line 52 (parse open price with MAX_OPEN_PRICE_AGE_SECS = 60s)\n- `settle_round` → line 87 (parse close price with MAX_CLOSE_PRICE_AGE_SECS = 120s)\n\n---\n\n### 4. Shared Crate Usage\n\nAll usages of `rng_shared::` found in closecall program:\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/lib.rs` exports these modules:\n- `commit_reveal`\n- `constants`\n- `escrow`\n- `fairness`\n- `fees`\n- `lifecycle`\n- `pause`\n- `wager`\n- `timeout`\n- `vrf_orao` (feature-gated)\n\n**Closecall imports** (from grep results):\n\n| Import | File:Line | Function Used | Purpose |\n|--------|-----------|---------------|---------|\n| `rng_shared::pause::check_not_paused` | create_round.rs:2 | check_not_paused(false, paused) | Verify game not paused (line 48) |\n| `rng_shared::pause::check_not_paused` | place_bet.rs:3 | check_not_paused(false, paused) | Verify game not paused (line 37) |\n| `rng_shared::escrow::transfer_lamports_to_pda` | place_bet.rs:2 | transfer_lamports_to_pda(player, round, amount, system) | Deposit wager (line 83) |\n| `rng_shared::wager::validate_wager` | place_bet.rs:4 | validate_wager(amount) | Enforce min/max wager (line 45) |\n| `rng_shared::escrow::transfer_lamports_from_pda` | settle_round.rs:2 | transfer_lamports_from_pda(round, recipient, payout) | Pay winners + treasury (lines 167, 174, 191, 205) |\n| `rng_shared::fees::calculate_net_payout` | settle_round.rs:3 | calculate_net_payout(total_pool) | Compute fee & net payout (line 129) |\n| `rng_shared::escrow::transfer_lamports_from_pda` | timeout_refund.rs:2 | transfer_lamports_from_pda(round, player, amount) | Refund bets (lines 81, 91) |\n| `rng_shared::timeout::is_expired` | timeout_refund.rs:3 | is_expired(deadline, now) | Check deadline passed (line 57) |\n| `rng_shared::escrow::transfer_lamports_from_pda` | force_close.rs:2 | transfer_lamports_from_pda(round, player, amount) | Refund bets (lines 74, 84) |\n\n**Shared crate dependencies in Cargo.toml**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/Cargo.toml:12`\n```\nrng-shared = { workspace = true }\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Fee Calculation Logic\n\n**Location**: Shared crate at `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/fees.rs`\n\n**Constants** (lines 1-11):\n```rust\npub const MAX_FEE_BPS: u16 = 1000;          // Safety cap\npub const TOTAL_FEE_BPS: u16 = 300;         // 3%\npub const REVENUE_BPS: u16 = 200;           // 200 bps revenue\npub const RAKEBACK_BPS: u16 = 70;           // 70 bps rakeback\npub const CHEST_BPS: u16 = 30;              // 30 bps chest treasury\n```\n\n**Public Functions**:\n\n1. **`calculate_fee(amount: u64) -> u64`** (lines 18-20):\n   - Formula: `(amount * 300 / 10000)` — rounds down, favors player\n   - Used in: settle_round.rs:129 as `calculate_net_payout(total_pool)`\n\n2. **`calculate_net_payout(pool: u64) -> (u64, u64)`** (lines 25-28):\n   - Returns `(fee, net_payout)` where `net_payout = pool - fee`\n   - Called in settle_round handler (line 129)\n   - Fee goes to treasury; net_payout distributed to winners\n\n3. **`split_fee(fee: u64) -> (u64, u64, u64)`** (lines 31-36):\n   - Returns `(revenue, rakeback, chest)`\n   - Not currently used in closecall (future integration)\n   - Remainder goes to chest to avoid rounding loss\n\n**Integration in settle_round** (settle_round.rs:125-130):\n```rust\nlet total_pool = round.green_pool + round.red_pool;\nlet (fee, net_pool) = calculate_net_payout(total_pool);\ntotal_fee = fee;\n// ... distribute net_pool to winners\n// ... transfer fee to treasury (line 174)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 6. Phase/State Machine Enums\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/state.rs`\n\n**1. CloseCallPhase** (lines 12-19):\n```rust\npub enum CloseCallPhase {\n    Open,      // Round is open for bets (first 30s of candle)\n    Settled,   // Outcome determined, payouts distributed\n    Refunded,  // All bets refunded (invalid round, timeout, or force close)\n}\n```\n\n**Transitions**:\n- `Open` → `Settled` (settle_round handler, line 239) on decisive outcome\n- `Open` → `Refunded` (settle_round handler, line 237) on refund outcome\n- `Open` → `Refunded` (timeout_refund handler, line 96) on deadline elapsed\n- `Open` → `Refunded` (force_close handler, line 89) on admin force close\n\n**2. Outcome** (lines 23-28):\n```rust\npub enum Outcome {\n    Pending,  // Not yet determined\n    Green,    // Green (bull) side won\n    Red,      // Red (bear) side won\n    Refund,   // Refunded (invalid round, no winner, or timeout)\n}\n```\n\n**Determination logic** (settle_round.rs:108-117):\n```rust\nlet outcome = if total_count == 0 {\n    Outcome::Refund\n} else if !has_both_sides || total_count == 1 || close_price == open_price {\n    Outcome::Refund\n} else if close_price > open_price {\n    Outcome::Green\n} else {\n    Outcome::Red\n};\n```\n\n**3. BetSide** (lines 5-8):\n```rust\npub enum BetSide {\n    Green,  // Bull side\n    Red,    // Bear side\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. Error Codes\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/error.rs`\n\nAll error codes use `#[error_code]` which adds 6000 base offset (Anchor convention).\n\n| Error Code | Final Code | Message | Context |\n|-----------|-----------|---------|---------|\n| `WagerBelowMinimum = 100` | **6100** | \"Wager amount below minimum\" | place_bet validation (line 45) |\n| `InvalidPhase` | **6101** | \"Round is not in the expected phase\" | phase check (lines 40, 44, 62) |\n| `BettingClosed` | **6102** | \"Betting window has closed\" | time check (line 43) |\n| `PlayerAlreadyBet` | **6103** | \"Player already has a bet in this round\" | one-bet-per-player check (line 64) |\n| `MaxEntriesReached` | **6104** | \"Maximum entries per side reached\" | max_entries check (lines 71, 77) |\n| `InvalidSide` | **6105** | \"Invalid bet side: must be 0 (Green) or 1 (Red)\" | side validation (line 50) |\n| `CandleNotClosed` | **6106** | \"Candle has not closed yet\" | settle_round timing (line 83) |\n| `InvalidPriceAccount` | **6107** | \"Invalid Pyth price account data\" | pyth.rs deserialization (lines 65, 74) |\n| `PriceFeedMismatch` | **6108** | \"Pyth feed ID does not match expected feed\" | pyth.rs feed validation (line 69) |\n| `PriceTooStale` | **6109** | \"Price data is too stale\" | pyth.rs freshness check (line 74) |\n| `DeadlineNotReached` | **6110** | \"Resolve deadline has not elapsed yet\" | timeout_refund timing (line 58) |\n| `AccountMismatch` | **6111** | \"Account key does not match expected value\" | account validation (lines 70, 75, 149, 188) |\n| `ArithmeticOverflow` | **6112** | \"Arithmetic overflow\" | checked_add/sub/mul/div (lines 101, 127) |\n| `RemainingAccountsMismatch` | **6113** | \"Remaining accounts count does not match expected\" | settlement recipient count (lines 141, 181) |\n| `ExponentMismatch` | **6114** | \"Price exponent mismatch between open and close\" | pyth.rs exponent validation (line 97) |\n\n---\n\n### 8. PDA Seeds\n\n**Location**: Across instruction modules (grep results confirmed)\n\n| PDA Name | Seeds | File:Line(s) |\n|----------|-------|-------------|\n| **CloseCallConfig** | `[b\"closecall_config\"]` | initialize_config.rs:14, create_round.rs:26, place_bet.rs:16, settle_round.rs:32, timeout_refund.rs:26, force_close.rs:24 |\n| **CloseCallRound** | `[b\"cc_round\", &round_id]` | create_round.rs:35, place_bet.rs:23, settle_round.rs:26, timeout_refund.rs:19, force_close.rs:17 |\n\n**Usage**:\n- Config PDA: Initialized once (initialize_config), read-only in all other instructions\n- Round PDA: Created per round (create_round), mutated by place_bet, settled/closed by settle_round/timeout_refund/force_close\n\n---\n\n### 9. Max Entries Per Side Enforcement\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/instructions/place_bet.rs:66-80`\n\n**State Definition** (state.rs:71-74):\n```rust\n#[max_len(32)]\npub green_entries: Vec<BetEntry>,\n#[max_len(32)]\npub red_entries: Vec<BetEntry>,\n```\n\n**Validation Logic** (place_bet.rs:54, 66-80):\n```rust\nlet max_per_side = ctx.accounts.config.max_entries_per_side as usize;\n\nmatch bet_side {\n    BetSide::Green => {\n        require!(\n            ctx.accounts.round.green_entries.len() < max_per_side,\n            CloseCallError::MaxEntriesReached\n        );\n    }\n    BetSide::Red => {\n        require!(\n            ctx.accounts.round.red_entries.len() < max_per_side,\n            CloseCallError::MaxEntriesReached\n        );\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Configuration**:\n- Set during initialization via `initialize_config` instruction parameter (lib.rs:21, initialize_config.rs:27)\n- Stored in `CloseCallConfig.max_entries_per_side: u8` (state.rs:51)\n- Runtime limit enforced in place_bet (length check against config value)\n- Hard max in state via `#[max_len(32)]` — cannot exceed 32 per side\n\n---\n\n### 10. Timeout / Refund Logic\n\n**Location**: Multiple instruction files\n\n**A. Timeout Constants** (create_round.rs:12-16):\n```rust\npub const CANDLE_DURATION_SECS: i64 = 60;      // 1-minute candle\npub const RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS: i64 = 300;     // 5 minutes after candle close\n```\n\n**Total deadline** = `created_at + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS + RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS` = 360 seconds (6 minutes) from round creation\n\n**B. Timeline Setup** (create_round.rs:59-74):\n```rust\nlet betting_window = ctx.accounts.config.betting_window_secs as i64;\nround.created_at = now;\nround.betting_ends_at = now + betting_window;\nround.resolve_deadline = now + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS + RESOLVE_TIMEOUT_SECS;\n```\n\n**C. Settle Round Timing Check** (settle_round.rs:78-83):\n```rust\nlet now = Clock::get()?.unix_timestamp;\nlet candle_close_time = round.created_at + CANDLE_DURATION_SECS;\nrequire!(now >= candle_close_time, CloseCallError::CandleNotClosed);\n```\n- Must wait ≥ 60 seconds after round creation to settle\n\n**D. Timeout Refund Logic** (timeout_refund.rs:39-99):\n```rust\nlet now = Clock::get()?.unix_timestamp;\nrequire!(\n    is_expired(round.resolve_deadline, now),\n    CloseCallError::DeadlineNotReached\n);\n```\n- Uses `is_expired(deadline, now)` from `rng_shared::timeout` (returns `now >= deadline`)\n- If deadline passed and round still `Open`, anyone can call timeout_refund\n- Refunds all bets (green + red) in full\n- Sets phase to `Refunded`, outcome to `Outcome::Refund`\n\n**E. Refund Payouts** (settle_round.rs:176-211 and timeout_refund.rs:66-93):\n- Both handlers iterate green_entries first, then red_entries\n- Each player receives exact bet amount (no fees deducted on refund)\n- Remaining accounts list must match entry order: `[green_0..green_n, red_0..red_m]`\n- Account mismatch results in error 6111\n\n**F. Force Close** (force_close.rs:38-93):\n- Admin-only (requires config authority signature, line 11)\n- Identical to timeout_refund refund logic (no deadline check)\n- Can close `Open` rounds at any time\n- Sets phase to `Refunded`, outcome to `Outcome::Refund`\n\n---\n\n## Summary Statistics\n\n- **Instruction handlers**: 6 (initialize_config, create_round, place_bet, settle_round, timeout_refund, force_close)\n- **State structs**: 3 (CloseCallConfig, CloseCallRound, + 4 supporting enums)\n- **Error codes**: 15 (6100–6114)\n- **PDA types**: 2 (config, round)\n- **Max entries per side**: 32 (configurable at init, hard-capped in state)\n- **Candle duration**: 60 seconds\n- **Resolve timeout buffer**: 300 seconds (5 min after candle close)\n- **Fee structure**: 3% total (200 bps revenue, 70 bps rakeback, 30 bps chest)\n- **Shared crate modules used**: 5 (escrow, fees, pause, timeout, wager)\n- **Pyth parser functions**: 1 (parse_price_update)\n\nAll file paths are absolute and anchored to `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/` or `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/`."}],"totalDurationMs":99794,"totalTokens":61154,"totalToolUseCount":25,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":461,"cache_read_input_tokens":54719,"output_tokens":5974,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_inp