ndles from live Pyth price subscription\n- CloseCallRoundPage displays oracle-resolved prices from backend\n- No fallback mock mode present\n\n---\n\n### 10. **Wallet Integration — How `placeBet` Works**\n\n**Complete Flow:**\n\n```\nUser clicks GREEN/RED button\n  ↓ (SideSelector.tsx line 27, 43)\nhandlePlaceBetWithSide(side: BetSide)  [CloseCallPage.tsx:76-82]\n  ↓\nplaceBet(side)  [CloseCallContext.tsx:603-661]\n  ├─ Validate: wallet connected, side selected, amount in range\n  ├─ Validate: active round exists, phase === \"open\", time < bettingEndsAt\n  ├─ Validate: balance sufficient\n  ├─ Call buildPlaceBetTx()  [line 632-637]\n  │   ├─ Derive config PDA: [\"closecall_config\"]  [line 177]\n  │   ├─ Derive round PDA: [\"cc_round\", roundIdBytes]  [line 181]\n  │   ├─ Build placeBet instruction [line 186-194]:\n  │   │   accounts: player, config, round, systemProgram\n  │   │   args: roundIdBytes[], sideValue (0=green, 1=red), amountLamports\n  │   ├─ Create Transaction, set feePayer + recentBlockhash  [line 196-198]\n  │   └─ Return transaction\n  ├─ Call sendAndConfirm(transaction)  [line 640]\n  │   ├─ Pre-flight simulation + error parsing  [line 516-539]\n  │   ├─ Up to 3 send attempts with blockhash retry  [line 541-593]\n  │   ├─ Wait for confirmation (30s timeout)  [line 561-564]\n  │   ├─ Fallback status check on timeout  [line 574-582]\n  │   └─ Return signature\n  ├─ Clear pendingSide on success  [line 643]\n  ├─ Refresh round state  [line 646]\n  └─ Catch + parse error, refresh on race condition  [line 647-655]\n```\n\n**Transaction Building Details (buildPlaceBetTx, lines 169-201):**\n- Anchor program method: `.placeBet(roundIdBytes[], sideValue, amountLamports)`\n- Accounts strict: `{ player, config, round, systemProgram }`\n- Round ID is 8-byte hex string → converted to `number[]` array\n- Amount converted to BN (big number) for lamports precision\n- Transaction signed and confirmed via wallet adapter\n\n**Error Handling (parseTransactionError, lines 207-243):**\n- User rejected / cancelled\n- Insufficient funds (0x1 error)\n- BettingClosed / BettingWindowClosed\n- AlreadyBet / MaxEntriesReached\n- Game paused\n- Invalid phase\n- Network errors\n- Simulation failures\n- Blockhash expiry\n\n**Retry Logic (sendAndConfirm, lines 509-598):**\n- MAX_SEND_ATTEMPTS = 3\n- Caches first blockhash\n- On confirmation timeout (30s), checks signature status\n- Retries only on expired/aborted with fresh blockhash\n- Refreshes wallet balance on success\n\n---\n\n### Summary Statistics\n\n| Metric | Count |\n|--------|-------|\n| Total components | 6 |\n| Total files | 12 |\n| Total lines of code | ~2,000+ |\n| Context effects | 6 major effects |\n| API endpoints | 2 (current-round, history) |\n| State properties | 15+ |\n| Type definitions | 8 interfaces + 3 unions |\n| Constants | 9 major |\n| Payout calculator functions | 7 |\n\nAll files are **ready for integration** with the on-chain Close Call program. No breaking changes or missing pieces detected."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a1c00fb480923a347 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 78388\ntool_uses: 24\nduration_ms: 88370</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"efe120e9-7ceb-4e75-b227-230da807bdef","uuid":"7edab7d4-8a20-4267-bb67-37267e2a4863","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Thoroughly inventory the Close Call frontend code. Search in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/`. I need:\n\n1. All components in `features/close-call/` — list each file with its exports and line numbers for key functions/components\n2. Context provider — read `features/close-call/context/CloseCallContext.tsx` — what does it export? What API calls does it make? What wallet integration does it have?\n3. Types — read `features/close-call/types.ts` — list all types, interfaces, constants with line numbers\n4. Pages — check for `CloseCallPage.tsx` and `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` in `pages/`\n5. Route registration — grep for 