close price, no fee collected\n- Line 775: `one-sided pool (all green) — full refund, no fee` — Tests refund when only one side has bets\n- Line 808: `single player — full refund, no fee` — Tests refund for single player round\n- Line 830: `no bets — clean close` — Tests settlement of round with no bets, verifies PDA closure\n- Line 854: `rejects settlement before candle close` — Validates CandleNotClosed error code\n\n#### Subsuite: `timeout_refund` (line 880)\n- Line 881: `refunds all players after resolve deadline` — Tests timeout refund after deadline, verifies all players receive refunds, PDA closure\n- Line 915: `rejects before resolve deadline` — Validates DeadlineNotReached error code\n\n#### Subsuite: `force_close` (line 940)\n- Line 941: `admin force-closes and refunds all players` — Tests authority-only force close, verifies all players refunded, PDA closure\n- Line 965: `rejects non-admin caller` — Validates ConstraintHasOne (2001) error for non-authority caller\n\n**Status**: All tests are designed to pass; no skip flags observed. Program follows commit-reveal pattern with Pyth oracle integration.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Devnet E2E Tests\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/devnet/closecall-lifecycle.spec.ts`\n\n**Test Suite**: `closecall devnet oracle E2E` (line 206)\n\n- Line 222: `closecall infra: program deployed, Pyth readable, backend API responding` \n  - Checks: Program deployed & executable, Pyth BTC/USD account readable, backend `/closecall/current-round` and `/closecall/history` endpoints responding, sample round data shape\n  - Skip condition: If `VITE_CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID` not set\n\n- Line 288: `closecall lifecycle: bet both sides → settlement → verify`\n  - Full lifecycle test: wait for bettable round → Player A bets GREEN → Player B bets RED → wait for settlement → verify outcome/fees → check round details page\n  - Phases: round wait (90s timeout) → betting (12s min window) → settlement (120s timeout) → verification\n  - Checks: Wallet funding (0.1 SOL min), console error filtering, bet registration on-chain, settlement data accuracy\n  - Skip condition: If `VITE_CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID` not set OR no bettable round within 90s (Pyth devnet price staleness)\n\n**Status**: Conditional pass/skip. Requires devnet setup with Pyth oracle, funded player wallets, and backend running. Tests are designed to handle stale Pyth prices gracefully (skips lifecycle if no active round).\n\n---\n\n### 3. Visual/Route Tests\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/routes.spec.ts`\n\n**Test Suite**: `Route baselines` (implied describe block)\n\n- Line 19: `close call page`\n  - Navigates to `/close-call`, captures full-page screenshot for baseline comparison\n  - Snapshot: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/routes.spec.ts/close-call.png` (108 KB, updated 2026-03-18 05:23)\n\n- Line 24: `close call round page`\n  - Navigates to `/close-call/abc123`, captures full-page screenshot for baseline comparison\n  - Snapshot: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/routes.spec.ts/close-call-round.png` (89 KB, updated 2026-03-18 05:36)\n\n**Status**: Baseline visual regression tests. Pass condition: no pixel difference from baseline snapshot.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Visual/State Tests\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/states.spec.ts`\n\n**Test Suite**: `Close Call page` (line 198, nested within larger state test describe)\n\n- Line 199: `wallet disconnected`\n  - Clears mock wallet, navigates to `/close-call`, captures screenshot of disconnected state\n  - Snapshot: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/states.spec.ts/closecall-disconnected.png` (107 KB, updated 2026-03-18 05:37)\n\n- Line 207: `wallet connected`\n  - Clears mock wallet, navigates to `/close-call`, clicks wallet connect button, wai