{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Lg4coiSofAzCjmSk3kPqQw","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→import type { Round, PlayerBet } from \"../types\";\n     2→import { SIDE_COLORS, PLATFORM_FEE, BETTING_WINDOW_MS } from \"../types\";\n     3→\n     4→interface ActiveBetViewProps {\n     5→  round: Round;\n     6→  userBet: PlayerBet;\n     7→}\n     8→\n     9→export function ActiveBetView({ round, userBet }: ActiveBetViewProps) {\n    10→  // Calculate potential payout\n    11→  const winningPool = userBet.side === \"green\" ? round.pool.greenPool : round.pool.redPool;\n    12→  const totalPool = round.pool.totalPool;\n    13→  const netPool = totalPool * (1 - PLATFORM_FEE);\n    14→\n    15→  const potentialPayout = winningPool > 0 ? (userBet.amount / winningPool) * netPool : 0;\n    16→  const potentialProfit = potentialPayout - userBet.amount;\n    17→  const multiplier = userBet.amount > 0 ? potentialPayout / userBet.amount : 0;\n    18→\n    19→  // Get side color\n    20→  const sideColor = SIDE_COLORS[userBet.side];\n    21→\n    22→  // Determine if still in betting window (round is open and betting time hasn't elapsed)\n    23→  const isBettingOpen = round.phase === \"open\" && Date.now() < round.bettingEndsAt;\n    24→  const isLocked = round.phase === \"open\" && Date.now() >= round.bettingEndsAt;\n    25→\n    26→  // Phase display text\n    27→  const getPhaseText = () => {\n    28→    if (round.phase === \"settled\") return \"Round complete\";\n    29→    if (round.phase === \"refunded\") return \"Round refunded\";\n    30→    if (isBettingOpen) return \"Waiting for candle...\";\n    31→    if (isLocked) return \"Bets locked - watching candle...\";\n    32→    return \"\";\n    33→  };\n    34→\n    35→  // Time remaining in betting window\n    36→  const bettingTimeLeft = Math.max(0, round.bettingEndsAt - Date.now());\n    37→  const bettingProgress = 1 - bettingTimeLeft / BETTING_WINDOW_MS;\n    38→\n    39→  return (\n    40→    <div className=\"close-call-active-bet\">\n    41→      <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__header\">\n    42→        <h3 className=\"close-call-active-bet__title\">Your Active Bet</h3>\n    43→        <span\n    44→          className=\"close-call-active-bet__phase\"\n    45→          data-phase={round.phase}\n    46→          data-betting={isBettingOpen ? \"true\" : undefined}\n    47→          data-locked={isLocked ? \"true\" : undefined}\n    48→        >\n    49→          {getPhaseText()}\n    50→        </span>\n    51→      </div>\n    52→\n    53→      <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__card\">\n    54→        <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__side\" style={{ color: sideColor }}>\n    55→          <span className=\"close-call-active-bet__side-icon\">\n    56→            {userBet.side === \"green\" ? \"▲\" : \"▼\"}\n    57→          </span>\n    58→          <span className=\"close-call-active-bet__side-label\">\n    59→            {userBet.side.toUpperCase()}\n    60→          </span>\n    61→        </div>\n    62→\n    63→        <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__details\">\n    64→          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__row\">\n    65→            <span>Your Stake</span>\n    66→            <span>{userBet.amount.toFixed(4)} SOL</span>\n    67→          </div>\n    68→          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__row\">\n    69→            <span>Your Share</span>\n    70→            <span>\n    71→              {winningPool > 0\n    72→                ? ((userBet.amount / winningPool) * 100).toFixed(1)\n    73→                : 0}%\n    74→            </span>\n    75→          </div>\n    76→          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__row close-call-active-bet__row--highlight\">\n    77→            <span>Potential Win</span>\n    78→            <span className=\"close-call-active-bet__payout\">\n    79→              {potentialPayout.toFixed(4)} SOL\n    80→              <span className=\"close-call-active-bet__profit\">\n    81→                (+{potentialProfit.toFixed(4)})\n    82→              </span>\n    83→            </span>\n    84→          </div>\n    85→          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__row\">\n    86→            <span>Multiplier</span>\n    87→            <span style={{ color: sideColor }}>{multiplier.toFixed(2)}x</span>\n    88→          </div>\n    89→        </div>\n    90→      </div>\n    91→\n    92→      {isBettingOpen && (\n    93→        <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__note\">\n    94→          Your odds may change as more bets come in ({Math.ceil(bettingTimeLeft / 1000)}s left)\n    95→          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__progress\" style={{ width: `${bettingProgress * 100}%` }} />\n    96→        </div>\n    97→      )}\n    98→\n    99→      {isLocked && (\n   100→        <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__note close-call-active-bet__note--locked\">\n   101→          Odds are now locked. Good luck!\n   102→        </div>\n   103→      )}\n   104→    </div>\n   105→  );\n   106→}\n   107→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"efe120e9-7ceb-4e75-b227-230da807bdef","uuid":"c06a89c8-58d8-4848-88ca-52e73aa28a9b","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/components/ActiveBetView.tsx","content":"import type { Round, PlayerBet } from \"../types\";\nimport { SIDE_COLORS, PLATFORM_FEE, BETTING_WINDOW_MS } from \"../types\";\n\ninterface ActiveBetViewProps {\n  round: Round;\n  userBet: PlayerBet;\n}\n\nexport function ActiveBetView({ round, userBet }: ActiveBetViewProps) {\n  // Calculate potential payout\n  const winningPool = userBet.side === \"green\" ? round.pool.greenPool : round.pool.redPool;\n  const totalPool = round.pool.totalPool;\n  const netPool = totalPool * (1 - PLATFORM_FEE);\n\n  const potentialPayout = winningPool > 0 ? (userBet.amount / winningPool) * netPool : 0;\n  const potentialProfit = potentialPayout - userBet.amount;\n  const multiplier = userBet.amount > 0 ? potentialPayout / userBet.amount : 0;\n\n  // Get side color\n  const sideColor = SIDE_COLORS[userBet.side];\n\n  // Determine if still in betting window (round is open and betting time hasn't elapsed)\n  const isBettingOpen = round.phase === \"open\" && Date.now() < round.bettingEndsAt;\n  const isLocked = round.phase === \"open\" && Date.now() >= round.bettingEndsAt;\n\n  // Phase display text\n  const getPhaseText = () => {\n    if (round.phase === \"settled\") return \"Round complete\";\n    if (round.phase === \"refunded\") return \"Round refunded\";\n    if (isBettingOpen) return \"Waiting for candle...\";\n    if (isLocked) return \"Bets locked - watching candle...\";\n    return \"\";\n  };\n\n  // Time remaining in betting window\n  const bettingTimeLeft = Math.max(0, round.bettingEndsAt - Date.now());\n  const bettingProgress = 1 - bettingTimeLeft / BETTING_WINDOW_MS;\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"close-call-active-bet\">\n      <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__header\">\n        <h3 className=\"close-call-active-bet__title\">Your Active Bet</h3>\n        <span\n          className=\"close-call-active-bet__phase\"\n          data-phase={round.phase}\n          data-betting={isBettingOpen ? \"true\" : undefined}\n          data-locked={isLocked ? \"true\" : undefined}\n        >\n          {getPhaseText()}\n        </span>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__card\">\n        <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__side\" style={{ color: sideColor }}>\n          <span className=\"close-call-active-bet__side-icon\">\n            {userBet.side === \"green\" ? \"▲\" : \"▼\"}\n          </span>\n          <span className=\"close-call-active-bet__side-label\">\n            {userBet.side.toUpperCase()}\n          </span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__details\">\n          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__row\">\n            <span>Your Stake</span>\n            <span>{userBet.amount.toFixed(4)} SOL</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__row\">\n            <span>Your Share</span>\n            <span>\n              {winningPool > 0\n                ? ((userBet.amount / winningPool) * 100).toFixed(1)\n                : 0}%\n            </span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__row close-call-active-bet__row--highlight\">\n            <span>Potential Win</span>\n            <span className=\"close-call-active-bet__payout\">\n              {potentialPayout.toFixed(4)} SOL\n              <span className=\"close-call-active-bet__profit\">\n                (+{potentialProfit.toFixed(4)})\n              </span>\n            </span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__row\">\n            <span>Multiplier</span>\n            <span style={{ color: sideColor }}>{multiplier.toFixed(2)}x</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {isBettingOpen && (\n        <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__note\">\n          Your odds may change as more bets come in ({Math.ceil(bettingTimeLeft / 1000)}s left)\n          <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__progress\" style={{ width: `${bettingProgress * 100}%` }} />\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {isLocked && (\n        <div className=\"close-call-active-bet__note close-call-active-bet__note--locked\">\n          Odds are now locked. Good luck!\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n","numLines":107,"startLine":1,"totalLines":107}}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_011fmsFoZduddJpzWga6iHB3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have clear evidence for the remaining uncertain items:\n\n**FR-1 criterion 6: \"Clear label showing which candle the bet applies to\"**\nLines 225-232 of CloseCallPage.tsx show a banner: \"Will the current candle close GREEN or RED?\" — This IS a clear label showing the bet applies to the current candle. SATISFIED. Evidence: CloseCallPage.tsx:225-232.\n\n**FR-2 criterion 8: \"UI shows 'needs bets on both sides to activate' when pool is one-sided\"**\nLooking at PoolDistribution.tsx — it shows pool percentages, amounts, and odds but there's NO specific message about needing bets on both sides. \n\nThe component displays 50%/50% when empty but doesn't have a message like \"needs bets on both sides to activate\". GAP.\n\n**FR-7 criterion 6: \"Countdown timer showing betting window remaining\"**\nActiveBetView.tsx line 94 shows a countdown timer displaying seconds remaining, but this only appears after placing a bet. Before the user commits, I need to check if CloseCallPage.tsx provides any countdown visibility through the isBettingOpen variable.\n\nLooking at the sidebar components—BetAmountInput, SideSelector, PoolDistribution, Round Info—there's no countdown timer visible in the pre-bet state. The timer only shows up in ActiveBetView once you've placed a bet, which means players who haven't bet yet have no way to see how much time remains. This is a moderate gap since the countdown should be visible to everyone, not just active bettors. ActiveBetView isn't actually rendered anywhere in CloseCallPage, so there's a gap—players never see the countdown timer even though the component has one. The only timing indicators are the disabled button state and the chart's progress visualization, neither of which explicitly shows how much betting time remains. I should check if CandlestickChart displays any timer information itself. The active stake display is actually satisfied through PoolDistribution rather than ActiveBetView — it shows the user's bet side, amount, and potential payout when a bet exists. So I can mark FR-7 criterion 5 as satisfied. Now let me compile the full audit results across all functional requirements. NewRound\n6. Clear label showing which candle ✓ — CloseCallPage.tsx:225-232 \"Will the current candle close GREEN or RED?\"\n\n**FR-2:**\n1. GREEN/RED options ✓ — BetSide enum + SideSelector.tsx\n2. Flexible bet amount with 1/2, x2, MAX ✓ — BetAmountInput.tsx adjustBetAmount\n3. Min bet 0.001 SOL ✓ — types.ts MIN_BET_AMOUNT=0.001 + shared validate_wager\n4. Max bet 100 SOL ✓ — types.ts MAX_BET_AMOUNT=100 + shared validate_wager\n5. One bet per player per round ✓ — place_bet.rs PlayerAlreadyBet check\n6. Bets are locked once placed with no ability to modify or cancel ✓ — no cancel instruction\n7. Max 32 entries per side ✓ — state.rs max_len(32) + place_bet.rs runtime check\n8. UI shows \"needs bets on both sides\" — GAP, PoolDistribution doesn't show this message\n\n**FR-3 through FR-6:** All criteria satisfied across these features.\n\n**FR-7:** The main display includes a large candlestick chart with the current candle highlighted, paired with a betting panel containing amount input controls and side selection buttons.\n\nLooking at the remaining items, I see the pool distribution component displays both pool sizes and active stakes with percentage breakdowns. The resolution animation plays when the round ends, and the outcome is clearly communicated through the result banner. However, there's a countdown timer in the codebase that isn't currently being rendered in the main betting view, so players don't see how much time remains in the betting window. Additionally, the UI doesn't explicitly tell players when they need to place bets on both sides of a pool.\n\nOverall, 39 out of 41 criteria are satisfied, with 2 gaps identified: the missing countdown timer display and the missing validation message for incomplete bets. I need to correct my earlier assessment about RoundResultOverlay — it's actually not being used in CloseCallPage. The page imports RoundResultBanner from the UI library instead, which handles the resolution animation and displays the outcome text, player result, and payout amount. So FR-7 criteria 7 and 8 are both satisfied by this component. Now I can finalize the gap analysis report and update the spec.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":15895,"cache_read_input_tokens":73094,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":15895},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"efe120e9-7ceb-4e75-b227-230da807bdef","uuid":"a4d21ef2-d879-48e0-b594-07488037e99a"}
